==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Porterage
<hw>Por"ter*age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
work of a porter; the occupation of a carrier or of a
doorkeeper.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Money charged or paid for the carriage of burdens or
parcels by a porter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Porteress</ent>⟦br⟧
